                  <join result="offencePlace" targOrder="Y" targets="t18211205-173-off1065 t18211205-173-crimeloc1068"></join>. On the 1st. of November, about six o'clock in the evening, we had a sale of wine; my business was to supply the Company with samples, and observing the glasses decrease, my suspicion fell on the prisoner, we stopped him as he went out; I took fourteen glasses from his pockets.</p>
